Class
	tnbLib::functionObjects::Q

Description
	Calculates and outputs the second invariant of the velocity gradient tensor
	[1/s^2].

	\f[
		Q = 0.5(sqr(tr(\nabla U)) - tr(((\nabla U) \cdot (\nabla U))))
	\f]

